We are looking for a creative and passionate Marketing Executive to take charge of developing the clients’ brand and marketing strategies. The Marketing Executive will co-create the company’s projected brand and consider their customer's perspectives and the company’s desired image and priorities. This includes the development and execution of branding campaigns, public relations and reputation management strategies to sustain or enhance the desired brand. He/she will also develop the marketing strategy for delivering consistent messaging through content on various platforms, including the conceptualisation and development of content to attract and engage target audience.

The core role of the Marketing Executive will be to deliver the design and copywriting of brand creatives and collaterals, and execute branding campaigns and activities that incorporate the internal and external stakeholders’ perspectives and responses.

*Fresh graduates are welcome to apply*